snippet: Courtney Walker scored 17 points while Taylor Cooper added 11 to help No. 5 Texas A&M escape Texas-Pan American's upset bid with a 63-61 victory on Sunday....

headline.print_headline: Walker Helps No. 5 Texas A&M Hold Off UTPA 63-61
headline.main: Walker Helps No. 5 Texas A&M Hold Off UTPA 63-61

lead_paragraph: Courtney Walker scored 17 points while Taylor Cooper added 11 to help No. 5 Texas A&M escape Texas-Pan American's upset bid with a 63-61 victory on Sunday.
